Package: phylospatial
Title: Tools for spatial phylogenetic analysis
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Authors@R: 
    person("Matthew", "Kling", , "mkling@uvm.edu", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0001-9073-4240"))
Description: This package computes a variety of spatial phylogenetic metrics, using data on a phylogenetic tree and the geographic distributions of the terminal taxa. Functionality includes diversity and endemism metrics, turnover and biotic regionalization analyses, null model randomizations, and spatial conservation prioritization. All functions support quantitative community data in addition to binary data.
